title: Rizzles Cafe and Dulceria
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Italian, Fast food, Salad bar, Juice bar, Take-out, European, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Casual cafe up the street from the bus terminal on Main Gate Street, Victoria, Gozo Island. Offers a wide variety salads, some of which are vegetarian and vegan suitable. Be clear when specifying which salads you'd like so the staff doesn't put meat ones on your plate. Makes fresh orange juice.
streetAddress: Main Gate Street, St. Francis Square
